.000Z","msg":"屌唔好下下都叫學生去做好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n個香港你冇份嘅？ <br />\n <br />\n衝又過叫d細嘅衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算ocamp都係輕鬆下有乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n依家個局勢咁樣真係要balance下<br />\n<br />\n下下chur到個人咁緊唔係好事<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做 長期抗爭 遍地開花"},{"pid":"52842742d9b2d51589fa191b396784005cb4f798","tid":1298243,"uid":96032,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:26:39.000Z","msg":"點解講到成個運動係得學生搞咁？<br />\n成個連登咁多人，呢兩個月9成post都係講緊場運動，全撚部都係學生？<br />\n點解要將所有嘢推曬落班學生到？<br />\n如果成場運動真係由學生主導，咁大家係咪應該檢討下？<br />\n平時就話90後00後又奶共又點，有事就推曬畀佢哋<br />\n唔該唔好再貼標籤落學生到，呢場係所有香港人嘅運動，我哋要證明各個年齡層都有參與其中，先有說服力證明呢個係主流民意，唔會再畀班藍絲廢中用「班廢青心智未成熟，容易被人洗腦」嚟做藉口"},{"pid":"22c0dd519d8fcfe256385dedb701b25b502ad49d","tid":1298243,"uid":13343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:28:23.000Z","msg":"反國教嗰年好多大學ocamp都有去政總"},{"pid":"759d108f8ea37074bb34611618128c317b39f00a","tid":1298243,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:29:59.000Z","msg":"OCAMP當然係同後輩介紹下香港大學既優良抗爭傳統文化"},{"pid":"603cea57023fed8a0afca94a42979fe7c04c0fb1","tid":1298243,"uid":138420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:31:36.000Z","msg":"你地都傻既 企最前個堆大學生黎架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔玩ocamp 無人上莊 呢堆學運傳統就斷架啦 <br />\n個個讀死書有鬼用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7517189df16362107c44f5b44ba5a82362a43d1","tid":1298243,"uid":5945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d22c2b7850a2257818b1e326cc738c3b296834e","tid":1298243,"ui